Now don't get me
in no trouble.

35
00:01:58.910 --> 00:02:01.913
[♪ Jazz piano music playing]

36
00:02:05.917 --> 00:02:08.253
[Rue] <i>He may have been
ugly on the outside.</i>

37
00:02:08.337 --> 00:02:10.547
<i>but on the inside.
he was a good man.</i>

38
00:02:10.631 --> 00:02:12.674
Heavenly Father.
thank you for the food

39
