00:03:12.984 --> 00:03:15.111
<i>- ♪ Go down ♪
- ♪ Go down ♪</i>

58
00:03:15.195 --> 00:03:17.488
<i>- ♪ Moses ♪
- ♪ Moses ♪</i>

59
