Homework. not cowboys.

125
00:06:12.247 --> 00:06:14.165
Hey. [laughing]

126
00:06:15.083 --> 00:06:17.878
Yes.
Mm-hmm.

127
00:06:18.712 --> 00:06:19.838
Soon. love.

128
00:06:20.755 --> 00:06:22.507
You'll see.
Red box.

129
00:06:24.509 --> 00:06:25.760
Middle drawer.

130
00:06:27.345 --> 00:06:28.638
[Laughing]

131
00:06:28.722 --> 00:06:30.640
