So what was
your favorite part? Hm?

147
00:07:13.183 --> 00:07:15.560
The beach or...

148
00:07:21.232 --> 00:07:22.609
Oh. my God.

149
00:07:29.115 --> 00:07:32.494
Oh. my God.
Oh. my God.

150
00:07:33.453 --> 00:07:35.997
